high_descs: Turn around and walk right, all the way to the blue bin in the corner.
Take the pencil out of the bin.
Turn around and veer right, walking around the bed to the circular table next to it on the left side.
Place the pencil on the table, to the left side of the CD.
anns.task_desc: Place a pencil on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the recycle bin.
Pick up the pencil from inside the bin.
Carry the pencil and turn around. Move forward and then turn left and locate the small round table. Turn right to face it.
Place the pencil on the table, towards the front right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil to the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the blue bin on the floor across the room near the wall.
Pick up the pencil from inside the blue bin on the floor.
Turn around, hang a right at the black chairs, turn left at the door and walk to the side of the small round table on the right.
Put the pencil to the right of the lamp on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pencil on a table.
